```plantuml
@startuml AhmedAbdelGawadFarag_Shams-Personal-Assistant
actor User
participant "Android App" as AndroidApp
participant "Main Server" as MainServer
participant "NER Server" as NERServer
participant "Google Cloud STT" as GoogleSTT
participant "Google Cloud TTS" as GoogleTTS

User -> AndroidApp: Speaks command (Arabic)
AndroidApp -> GoogleSTT: Convert speech to text
GoogleSTT --> AndroidApp: Returns text
AndroidApp -> MainServer: Send text command
MainServer -> NERServer: Extract named entities
NERServer --> MainServer: Returns entities
MainServer -> MainServer: Classify intent
MainServer -> MainServer: Execute business logic
MainServer -> GoogleTTS: Convert response to speech
GoogleTTS --> MainServer: Returns audio
MainServer --> AndroidApp: Send response (text + audio)
AndroidApp -> User: Play audio response
@enduml
```